<h1 class="text-4xl text-center font-serif mb-8 hinge-header">
  Our Story
</h1>

<p class="mt-4 mb-4">
  Our story, like so many of the modern age, began on the dating app Hinge.
  Cozied up with family over the holidays of 2021
  vented to her sisters: "I'm only meeting people of low quality and I don't know
  why!" she exclaimed. Susan and Karen, always there to
  be Helen's guiding compass, took a look at her profile; they were apalled by what
  they found.
</p>
<p class="mt-4 mb-4">
  "No wonder you're only matching with miscreants. A profile like this is no
  good!" You've got to fully represent yourself and put the energy out
  there that you want to find, a nerdy, athletic, honest person." They decalred.
  Unable to tolerate the mess before them, Susan and Karen joined forces, and
  together with the power of sisterhood they channeled their lifelong knowledge
  and love of Helen's essence to perform a Cinderellian transformation of
  Helen's Hinge profile.
</p>

<p class="mt-4 mb-4">
  Naught but a few days later, Helen, on Saturday January 8th at 2:21 AM liked
  the profile of a cute a dashing young nerd named Adam. Our first conversation
  went like this:
</p>

