<p class="mt-4 mb-4">
  It was at this point in our Story that Helen thought to herself.
  <i>Huh I am not impressed with that typo, but maybe be with someone less detailed
    oriented than myself... And besides I already committed to a date.</i>
</p>

<p class="mt-4 mb-4">
  The date was set and the next night, Adam sent a quick check-in.
</p>

